        • synthType

          byte synthType
          Byte encoding:
          -1 - built in (Java)
          -2 - included (Python)
          -3 - project specific (Python)
          64+ - reserved for user defined libraries (Python)

        • synthName

          java.lang.String synthName
          The synthesizer to be used for everything
          This may be shared
          Based on byte code: if built in, string is the name, otherwise it's a filename
